
## .gitignore

Use this:

```gitignore
# Compiled binaries
*.exe
*.out
*.app
*.o
*.obj

# Build folders
build/
bin/
debug/
release/

# CMake files, if added later
CMakeFiles/
CMakeCache.txt
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile

# IDE/editor files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sln
*.vcxproj
*.vcxproj.filters
*.user

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
